summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $29.32, or so much thereof as may be necessary, from the general fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of paying the 1910 general taxes on part of lot 24, block 3, Adam's 1st Addition to Fauntleroy Park, on a certain tract for street purposes in L. M. Collins Donation Claim \#46 and on a certain tract in section 5, township 25 north, range 4 east, W.M., for street purposes.
